V 1.3  -by Fleisar

CONFIGURATION FILE
/forum/modules/sqli.php [3-8]

CONFIGURATION MySQL
required database named 'forum'

PERMISSION LEVEL
set permission level can only in PMA (or other DB managers)
highest permission level: 1 (Moderator)
lower level: 0

What can moderator?
-delete comments users
-delete topics other users
-send comments via "send+"

What can user?
-create topics
-send comments (except "send+")